          <cite class="block text-right mt-4 font-semibold text-natural-beige not-italic">Keren â€“ Daughter</cite>
        </blockquote>
        
        <blockquote class="bg-coral-warmth text-white p-8 rounded-2xl relative text-xl leading-relaxed mt-8">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 text-6xl text-natural-beige opacity-75">"</div>
          Kelly has been giving neck, shoulder, back massages to my husband who has dementia for several months. Initially for 10 to 15 minutes, now increased to 45. He loves it. He becomes relaxed and mellow, and always looks forward to his treatments and chats with Kelly. I am very grateful for the pleasure and help she gives him, unwaveringly friendly, and coping admirably with a sometimes challenging client.
          <cite class="block text-right mt-4 font-semibold text-natural-beige not-italic">Pat - Wife</cite>
        </blockquote>
        
        <blockquote class="bg-dusty-rose text-slate-800 p-8 rounded-2xl relative text-xl leading-relaxed mt-8">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 text-6xl text-slate-600 opacity-75">"</div>
          Kelly is an incredibly bubbly, easy going but dedicated person. She puts her heart and sole into everything she sets out to achieve and works hard to make sure it happens. Kelly builds suitable relationships with everyone carefully and takes their needs and abilities into consideration. Kelly has a lot of patience and is good at understanding what individuals need and how to respond to various situations. Overall, Kelly is a wonderful person with lots of empathy and friendliness.
          <cite class="block text-right mt-4 font-semibold text-slate-600 not-italic">Amy â€“ Home Ambassador</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
